My "dreamapp"! Maven archetype that creates a bundled executable jetty java webapplication. Run jetty in four ways, as a maven jetty:run, as unit test in your IDE, as executable war or inside a appserver as a war. The application is a spring web/REST application backed by in memory datasource.

Heres how to create your "dreamapp":

git clone git://github.com/bjornno/dreamapp.git
cd dreamapp
mvn clean install
cd to directory where you want to create your app
mvn archetype:create -DarchetypeGroupId=bjornno.integration -DarchetypeArtifactId=integration-archetype -DarchetypeVersion=1.0-SNAPSHOT -DgroupId=<your group id> -DartifactId=<your artifact id>
cd <your artifact id>
mvn clean install
java -jar target/XXexecutable-war // or any of the other four ways you prefer..

